2:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"An internal auditor is appointed by the auditing committee in UAE who presents the reports to the board of directors (BOD). An internal auditor’s opinion is independent and they are directly answerable to the audit committee."}]
3:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms provides the best auditing services and one of the best auditing consultancies in Dubai."}]
4:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification in UAE is a most preferred Certification Standard by organizations in UAE from all sectors. Wizms provides ISO Certificate in UAE for all major standards such as ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015, ISO 27001:2015, ISO 17025:2017, ISO 45001:2018 and more. Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE and provides ISO consulting services in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. Wizms ISO consultant in Dubai offers top-class ISO consultancy services including ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO certification audits in UAE."}]
